name: Really Cheap Health Insurance
description: Cheap health insurance quotes and news
overview:
RCHI is a website designed designed to give average users access to easy-to-read articles on health insurance. Our health insurance articles are targeted to ordinary people, from young professionals to stay-at-home moms and seniors.

Soon we will also be able to add the car insurance segment on the site and we are excited about providing the same quality of articles, news and insurance quotes for car owners.

We can bring back affordable to health insurance. Take our 3-minute 1-2-3 progress or go deeper for a more specialized coverage. Also on site is our news section, updated by a long-time insurance professional. And once you’re all done, we would appreciate a brief testimonial. Any input is welcome.
